data.description: Beautiful 2-story home on Devine Golf Course - known as "The Castle House" in Devine - open floor plan - granite counter tops - cozy fireplace in living area - all bedrooms are upstairs - 2nd story balcony off of master suite and 2nd bedroom - beautiful views of golf course - very nice outdoor entertaining area off back patio - covered patio and additional rock patio area added for more seating and BBQ area - private water well for yard irrigation. Come see the charming home.
